sentences.original:
The following slight defects, however, may be allowed, provided these do not affect the general appearance of the produce, the quality, the keeping quality and presentation in the package:
- slight defects in shape;
- slight defects of the skin not exceeding 1 cm2 of the total surface area of the fruit.

The following defects, however, may be allowed, provided the pitahayas retain their essential characteristics as regards the quality, the keeping quality and presentation:
- defects in shape;
- defects of the skin not exceeding 2 cm2 of the total surface area of the fruit.
